docs.snippet: Several vessels of the Hamburg-American and North German Lloyd lines will be transferred as a result of the recent reorganization of their services abroad, it was announced yesterday. Two vessels, the Eupatoria and the General Osorio, will be...
docs.lead_paragraph: Several vessels of the Hamburg-American and North German Lloyd lines will be transferred as a result of the recent reorganization of their services abroad, it was announced yesterday. Two vessels, the Eupatoria and the General Osorio, will be transferred by the Hamburg-American to the Hamburg South American Line and ten more will be transferred later.
